    raw_context: dict
```

### MarketContext

```python
class MarketContext:
    coin: str
    ts_ms: int
    mid_px: float
    best_bid: float
    best_ask: float
    spread_bps: float
    depth_bid_usdc_10bps: float
    depth_ask_usdc_10bps: float
    estimated_slippage_bps: float
    recent_volatility_bps: float | None
    funding_rate: float | None
    open_interest: float | None
    raw_l2_book: dict
```

### EdgeEstimate

```python
class EdgeEstimate:
    signal_id: str
    expected_move_bps: float
    fees_bps: float
    spread_cost_bps: float
    slippage_bps: float
    latency_penalty_bps: float
    uncertainty_penalty_bps: float
    crowding_penalty_bps: float
    edge_remaining_bps: float
    accepted: bool
    reason: str
```

### PaperTrade

```python
class PaperTrade:
    id: str
    signal_id: str
    coin: str
    side: str
    entry_ts_ms: int
    entry_px_model: float
    entry_px_after_slippage: float
    size_usdc: float
    fees_usdc: float
    status: str  # OPEN | CLOSED | REJECTED | PARTIAL | EXPIRED
    exit_ts_ms: int | None
    exit_px_model: float | None
    exit_px_after_slippage: float | None
    realized_pnl_usdc: float | None
    pnl_after_costs_usdc: float | None
    mfe_bps: float | None
    mae_bps: float | None
```

